News.Content:

New maps! New format! More action!

News.Content:

- Battle Royale Duos: Jump into the fight with a friend!

News.Title: HUGE 1v1.LOL Update!
News.Content:
New Power Progression and Loadout Feature
Customize your weapon loadout and choose your arsenal

New Showdown Mode
Start each battle with your personal loadout and upgrade your weapons during the fight.

LOL Boxes
Collect them from winning games, through the Shop and Trophy Road to upgrade your power level and become ULTRA powerful!

Redesigned Trophy Road
Claim rank-up gifts directly! Unlock options to get new weapons and armors from LOL Boxes

Revamped Matchmaking
Prepare for more competitive and balanced matchups
